<div id="home">
  <% if visitor_signed_in? %>

    <h2>Welcome, <%= current_visitor.email %> </h2>

    <br>

    <a href = "https://rails-session.herokuapp.com/", target="blank">
      <button type="button" class="btn btn-warning">
        Previous Project
      </button>
    </a>

    <a href = "https://github.com/JuzerShakir/rails-authenticate", target="blank">
      <button type="button" class="btn btn-info">
        Source code
      </button>
    </a>

    <a href = "", target="blank">
      <button type="button" class="btn btn-success">
        Next Project
      </button>
    </a>

  <% else %>

    <h2>Hey Devs, Welcome to my Second Rails Project</h2>

    <p>In this project I have used 'devise' gem to help visitor signup, signin, logout and maintain a session in this webapp.</p>
    <p>Using devise, an additional feature of 'forgot password' is given. Visitor will recieve an email (using Action Mailer) with a link to reset the password.</p>

    <div class="note">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-7">
          <div class="alert-danger">
            <b>Note:</b> Sign up with an working email address as mails will be sent on that.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  <% end %>

  <div id="visitor-count">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-2.5">
        <div class="alert-info">
          Total visitors signed up: <b><%= @total %></b>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>

